  "texts": [
    "Lumini and Nanni (2019a); Lumini et al. (2020) evaluated various strategies for transfer learning on plankton images.",
    "The first strategy was to initialize the model with ImageNet weights and fine-tune the whole model with plankton data.",
    "In the second strategy (two rounds tuning), a second pre-training step utilizing out-of-domain plankton image data was added before the fine-tuning.",
    "In the third strategy, ensembles of multiple different models were used.",
    "Based on the experiments the two rounds tuning did not provide a notable improvement in accuracy."
  ],
